> The documentation says:
>=20
>   ADDV Rm, Rn        Rn + Rm -> Rn, overflow -> T
>=20
> But QEMU implementation was:
>=20
>   ADDV Rm, Rn        Rn + Rm -> Rm, overflow -> T
>=20
> Fix by filling the correct Rm register.
>=20
> Add tests provided by Paul Cercueil.
